en:
IMPORTANT: Include scene directives at the start of your response in this format:
[SCENE_DIRECTIVES]
{
  "mission_status": "ongoing",
  "characters": {
    "character_id": {"expression": "expression_type"}
  },
  "relationships": [
    {"source": "gloria", "target": "player", "status": "Disappointed", "value_change": -10}
  ]
}
[/SCENE_DIRECTIVES]

Available characters: protagonist, gloria, donkey, ark, one, teacher_chan
Available expressions: neutral, happy, sad, angry, confused, shocked, thinking, embarrassed
If relationships change, update them in relationships list with status string and value_change (-100 to 100).

**CRITICAL**: If this consequence resolves the current narrative arc (either as a catastrophic success or a failure), set "mission_status" to "complete". This triggers the end-of-mission sequence. Otherwise, keep it "ongoing".

zh:
請在回應開頭附上場景指令 JSON：
[SCENE_DIRECTIVES]
{
  "mission_status": "ongoing",
  "characters": {
    "character_id": {"expression": "expression_type"}
  },
  "relationships": [
    {"source": "gloria", "target": "player", "status": "失望", "value_change": -10}
  ]
}
[/SCENE_DIRECTIVES]

角色代號：protagonist, gloria, donkey, ark, one, teacher_chan
表情：neutral, happy, sad, angry, confused, shocked, thinking, embarrassed
若此事件改變了角色關係，請在 relationships 中更新狀態與數值（-100 到 100）。

**關鍵判斷**：如果這個後果代表當前單元故事的「結局」（無論是災難性的成功或徹底的失敗），請將 mission_status 設為 "complete"。這將會觸發故事的結算與進入下一章節。若故事仍在發展中，保持 "ongoing"。

de:
WICHTIG: Fuegen Sie Szenenanweisungen am Anfang Ihrer Antwort in diesem Format ein:
[SCENE_DIRECTIVES]
{
  "mission_status": "ongoing",
  "characters": {
    "character_id": {"expression": "expression_type"}
  },
  "relationships": [
    {"source": "gloria", "target": "player", "status": "Enttaeuscht", "value_change": -10}
  ]
}
[/SCENE_DIRECTIVES]

Verfuegbare Charaktere: protagonist, gloria, donkey, ark, one, teacher_chan
Verfuegbare Ausdruecke: neutral, happy, sad, angry, confused, shocked, thinking, embarrassed
Wenn sich Beziehungen aendern, aktualisieren Sie sie in der relationships-Liste mit status und value_change (-100 bis 100).

**KRITISCH**: Wenn diese Konsequenz den aktuellen Erzaehlbogen aufloest (als katastrophaler Erfolg oder Misserfolg), setzen Sie "mission_status" auf "complete". Andernfalls lassen Sie ihn auf "ongoing".

