en:
**IMPORTANT: Respond with EXACTLY one valid JSON object.**
Use this schema:
{
  "mission_title": "<Opening title, e.g., 'Welcome to the Glorious Deliverance Agency'>",
  "scene": {"background": "prayer", "atmosphere": "bright but unsettling", "lighting": "bright"},
  "characters": {
    "protagonist": {"expression": "confused", "visible": true},
    "gloria": {"expression": "happy", "visible": true},
    "donkey": {"expression": "happy", "visible": true},
    "ark": {"expression": "thinking", "visible": true},
    "one": {"expression": "neutral", "visible": true}
  },
  "story_text": "<200-300 word opening introduction>",
  "choices": [
    {"archetype": "cautious", "summary": "<Observe surroundings with suspicion>"},
    {"archetype": "positive", "summary": "<Express enthusiasm about joining>"},
    {"archetype": "balanced", "summary": "<Stay polite but guarded>"},
    {"archetype": "complain", "summary": "<Question the organization's true purpose>"}
  ]
}

The story_text must end with [Cautious], [Positive], [Balanced], [Complain] choice preview lines.

zh:
**重要：回應必須是有效 JSON 物件。**
輸出結構如下：
{
  "mission_title": "<開場標題，如「歡迎加入光榮拯救機構」>",
  "scene": {"background": "prayer", "atmosphere": "bright but unsettling", "lighting": "bright"},
  "characters": {
    "protagonist": {"expression": "confused", "visible": true},
    "gloria": {"expression": "happy", "visible": true},
    "donkey": {"expression": "happy", "visible": true},
    "ark": {"expression": "thinking", "visible": true},
    "one": {"expression": "neutral", "visible": true}
  },
  "story_text": "<200-300 字的開場介紹>",
  "choices": [
    {"archetype": "cautious", "summary": "<懷疑地觀察周圍>"},
    {"archetype": "positive", "summary": "<熱情地表示加入的決心>"},
    {"archetype": "balanced", "summary": "<禮貌但保持距離>"},
    {"archetype": "complain", "summary": "<質疑這個組織的真正目的>"}
  ]
}

story_text 結尾必須包含 [謹慎]、[樂觀]、[權衡]、[抱怨] 的選項預告行。

de:
**WICHTIG: Antworten Sie mit GENAU einem gueltigen JSON-Objekt.**
Verwenden Sie dieses Schema:
{
  "mission_title": "<Eroeffnungstitel, z. B. 'Willkommen bei der Glorious Deliverance Agency'>",
  "scene": {"background": "prayer", "atmosphere": "hell aber beunruhigend", "lighting": "bright"},
  "characters": {
    "protagonist": {"expression": "confused", "visible": true},
    "gloria": {"expression": "happy", "visible": true},
    "donkey": {"expression": "happy", "visible": true},
    "ark": {"expression": "thinking", "visible": true},
    "one": {"expression": "neutral", "visible": true}
  },
  "story_text": "<200-300 Woerter Eroeffnungseinleitung>",
  "choices": [
    {"archetype": "cautious", "summary": "<Umgebung misstrauisch beobachten>"},
    {"archetype": "positive", "summary": "<Begeisterung ueber den Beitritt ausdruecken>"},
    {"archetype": "balanced", "summary": "<Hoeflich bleiben, aber vorsichtig sein>"},
    {"archetype": "complain", "summary": "<Den wahren Zweck der Organisation infrage stellen>"}
  ]
}

story_text muss mit den Vorschauzeilen [Vorsichtig], [Positiv], [Ausgewogen] und [Beschweren] enden.
